WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:00.050
English Transcript Version Date: 2016-0326

00:07.617 --> 00:12.609
You have to put My Feet into your heart.

00:19.344 --> 00:23.258
Just My Feet into your heart.

00:25.188 --> 00:31.251
Because photo, face, everything might be an illusion.

00:33.530 --> 00:41.727
Might be, by seeing My Face you do not get over your barriers.

00:46.280 --> 00:50.571
To say, “I must see Mother. I must do this.

00:50.691 --> 00:54.664
Mother must come to my house. She must have food at my place.

00:54.784 --> 00:58.003
She must visit my home.” All this is so stupid.

00:58.124 --> 01:01.800
I cannot understand what’s the matter with these people.

01:07.948 --> 01:10.141
“Mother, please come in my heart.

01:10.261 --> 01:13.336
Let me clean my heart so that You are there.

01:13.456 --> 01:16.269
Put Your Feet into my heart.

01:18.792 --> 01:22.550
Let Your Feet be worshipped in my heart.

01:24.120 --> 01:27.597
Let me not be in delusion.

01:28.089 --> 01:31.594
Take me away from illusions.

01:31.714 --> 01:34.243
Keep me in reality.

01:34.363 --> 01:38.738
Take away the sheen of superficiality.

01:39.464 --> 01:43.391
Let me enjoy Your Feet in my heart.

01:43.511 --> 01:46.331
Let me see Your Feet in my heart.”
